{"tid":2127531,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［浸大人入嚟］點睇浸大炒邵膠樽？今日邵家臻 明日戴耀廷","createTime":"2020-07-27T11:16:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-28T10:55:06.000Z","uid":147786,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1c240afcea1fae77c736e9f1a8a3a7069b53cb3f","tid":2127531,"uid":147786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T11:16:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20200727/s00001/1595829140281/%e9%82%b5%e5%ae%b6%e8%87%bb%e4%b8%8d%e7%8d%b2%e6%b5%b8%e5%a4%a7%e7%ba%8c%e7%b4%84-%e7%a8%b1%e6%a0%a1%e6%96%b9%e7%84%a1%e6%8f%90%e4%be%9b%e5%8e%9f%e5%9b%a0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200727%2Fs00001%2F1595829140281%2F%25e9%2582%25b5%25e5%25ae%25b6%25e8%2587%25bb%25e4%25b8%258d%25e7%258d%25b2%25e6%25b5%25b8%25e5%25a4%25a7%25e7%25ba%258c%25e7%25b4%2584-%25e7%25a8%25b1%25e6%25a0%25a1%25e6%2596%25b9%25e7%2584%25a1%25e6%258f%2590%25e4%25be%259b%25e5%258e%259f%25e5%259b%25a0&d=ducsj56GsZITs%2BYA0ylwpbXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=8e30be98\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200727%2Fs00001%2F1595829140281%2F%25e9%2582%25b5%25e5%25ae%25b6%25e8%2587%25bb%25e4%25b8%258d%25e7%258d%25b2%25e6%25b5%25b8%25e5%25a4%25a7%25e7%25ba%258c%25e7%25b4%2584-%25e7%25a8%25b1%25e6%25a0%25a1%25e6%2596%25b9%25e7%2584%25a1%25e6%258f%2590%25e4%25be%259b%25e5%258e%259f%25e5%259b%25a0&h=3c6a2a44\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20200727/s00001/1595829140281/%e9%82%b5%e5%ae%b6%e8%87%bb%e4%b8%8d%e7%8d%b2%e6%b5%b8%e5%a4%a7%e7%ba%8c%e7%b4%84-%e7%a8%b1%e6%a0%a1%e6%96%b9%e7%84%a1%e6%8f%90%e4%be%9b%e5%8e%9f%e5%9b%a0</a><br />\n<br />\n//社福界立法會議員邵家臻原任浸會大學社工系講師，自去年佔中案被判囚後，浸大成立調查委員會進行紀律聆訊，邵家臻今早（27日）接獲院校電郵，稱其申請續約不獲批准，合約至下月31日到期，其他安排稍後通知，但並未提供理由。<br />\n<br />\n浸大回應表示，校方根據既定政策及程序處理所有合約事宜；基於私隱理由，校方不會透露個別個案的詳情。<br />\n<br />\n邵家臻向本報稱，相信原因是政治打壓、與佔中九子案相關，因浸大早前成立調查委員會，他上周五（24日）才呈交其陳述書，院校稱於8月24日有結果，但「現在都未完成件事，就炒了」。他稱，感覺是「要來的都要來」，仍然感到憤怒、不尊重，因浸大未有提供不續約的理由。<br />\n<br />\n邵家臻早於年初發現其教學工作被抽起後，向相關職員查詢，並與浸大社工系主任、人事部主管等人會面後，在會上接獲信件，稱他在本學期不需要教書，但仍具講師身分。//"},{"pid":"48e69d75136479ee6c5d9ea9d4303123c9de8fca","tid":2127531,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T11:57:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ff0847d864ef91892893e208b9fd7c17ea2d24f","tid":2127531,"uid":227813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T10:26:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86eff8d5a65cbf01ca1d8c983aea63f02512ecaa","tid":2127531,"uid":82938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T10:55:06.000Z","msg":"戴耀廷長工都比人炒硬<br />\n合約制更加啦<br />\n只可以去外國教"}]}